     C                     SETOF                     96
     C                     Z-ADD0         U       20
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    @KH
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    @KT
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    @KB
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    @KL
      *
