     C*--------------------------------*
     C*  ..部品マスター　構成品番..  *
     C*--------------------------------*
     C           *IN96     IFEQ '0'
     C                     Z-ADD1         V       20
     C           1         DO   4         V
     C           BKH,V     IFNE *BLANK
      *
     C                     MOVE BKH,V     #KHIN
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    @KH1
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    @KH2
     C                     MOVE #KHN1     @KHN1
     C                     MOVE #KHN2     @KHN2
     C                     MOVE #KHN3     @KHN3
      *
     C           #KHN2     IFNE *BLANK
     C                     MOVE '-'       @KH1
     C                     END
